title: MMDC - Find Dog Playdates
description:
Unleash your pet's social potential with MMDC, the ultimate dog meetup app. We're here to help your dog find their perfect puppy buddy and let them explore the vibrant dog-friendly community around them.

[Discover the Perfect Dog Friend]
Create a unique social profile for your dog and embark on an exciting new adventures and puppy socialization journey. Our tailored recommendations ensure that your dog finds the best match for their next playdate - considering size, breed, energy level, and more!

[Effortless Playdate Planning]

Your pet's new best buddy is only a like away! Search and explore nearby dogs and potential playdate locations directly on a map. Check detailed profiles to choose the perfect dog friend in your neighborhood, and plan 1:1 dog meetups with convenient in-chat reminders. Share your favorite dog-friendly parks, chat with other pawrents, and meet up for memorable experiences.

[Host & Attend Group Dog Playdates] 

Ready to host a dog meetup or puppy playdate? Use MMDC's advanced map to see nearby dogs and ideal playdate spots. Set a time and place, invite local pet parents, and let the fun begin! After the playdate, share a 'Playdate Memory' to capture the adventure and inspire others. Watch your dog‚Äôs social life soar as you build a collection of shared experiences.

[Create & Join in Dog Community Groups] 
Join MMDC‚Äôs Groups to connect with fellow dog lovers in your community. Form a puppy buddy group, arrange breed-specific meetups, or organize walking dates. Stay in the loop with group chats and updates on the group board ‚Äì your local dog community awaits!

[Connect with other dog parents]
Discover and share trusted dog services like daycares, groomers, vets, and favorite dog-friendly locations that other dog owners love. Leverage the wisdom of our dog community to fulfill your dog socialization needs and help your pet live its best life

Watch out, your dog is about to get a lot more social!
summary: Connect with nearby dog owners

title: PlayDates4Dogs
description:
PlayDates 4 Dogs (PD4D) is more than an app, it's a community of dog lovers! Download, connect and schedule your first Play date today. 

HOW IT WORKS
1. Download our FREE app
2. Sign up and create a profile for you and your furry friends
3. Schedule your Playdate
4. Enjoy and browse our online community with other dog lovers

OUR FEATURES 
You can browse by breed, age, weight, temperament, and more  
You can chat with other dog lovers and develop friendships outside our community
Send and receive messages through our secure app once you're connected.
summary: Doggy social network!

title: Dog Life Simulator
description:
Live the life of a dog and see the world through the eyes of your favourite pet! In this original narrative game the tables have turned and now it‚Äôs your turn to make the choices as this amazing animal!
Will you become man‚Äôs best friend and help your owner in their everyday life? Be a perfect pet companion, a puppy friend that everyone wishes they had?
Make choices that affect the outcome of your dog‚Äôs story! Care for your pet and make it the happiest puppy in the world! This is the virtual friend you‚Äôve been waiting for‚Ä¶ Seen from a completely different perspective.
Making good choices will earn you precious bones that you can use to upgrade your Dog‚Äôs kennel. This virtual animal will quickly become your best friend too!
This is a perfect game for all animal lovers! Download it now and find out for yourself!
summary: Perfect game for animal lovers! See the world through your dog‚Äôs eyes!

title: Dog Sim Online: Raise a Family
description:
Live the life of a dog in this online RPG adventure ‚Äì choose from your favorite dog breeds, explore a massive 3D world, and raise a family of puppies with Dog Sim!

Adventure as your favorite dog breeds in this new animal simulator. Join online multiplayer games to play with friends as you battle enemies and explore the 3D world. Build a family to pass on your genes and unlock all dog breeds to become the most powerful dog!

DOG SIM FEATURES:

3D SIMULATOR ‚Äì RAISE A FAMILY
- Animal breeding games: Bring 3D dogs to life with customizable breed, name and gender
- Build a family: Breed puppies to raise a whole family of dogs
- Puppies are new characters that you can play as and customize
- Unlock dog breeds with coins earned by leveling up and learn amazing facts about dogs
	
FANTASY RPG GAMEPLAY 
- Animal simulator: Fight, play and explore in this RPG animal simulator to feel what it‚Äôs like to be a dog!
- Adventure in this exciting simulation game, complete with multiple dog breeds to choose from
- Fight dangerous new bosses to protect your family and strengthen your dog
- Unlock fighting achievements by hunting specific enemies and leveling up

ONLINE MULTIPLAYER GAMES
- Multiplayer games let you explore with dogs from around the world for a fun online adventure!
- Adventure and play with friends to battle enemies and explore
- Battle in online multiplayer games to prove your strength in fighting 

ADVENTURE IN A REALISTIC 3D WORLD
- Adventure awaits in a whole new type of 3D map with 6 unique locations
- Explore the city or countryside, each with its own simulation of highly detailed, real weather conditions
- 3D markers let you easily navigate the world by zooming, rotating, and even using the compass
- Real online multiplayer: Face new enemies and make allies from around the world

WEATHER AND DAY/NIGHT CYCLE SIMULATOR
- Our simulator gives accurate weather with detailed levels of rainfall and thunder
- Play all day and night with a 24-hour based time system. For every minute played, a full in-game hour passes

CLANS and LEADERBOARDS
- Form clans and fight other online players in Clan Wars
- Leaderboards rank the best players by clan war points, level and duels
- See when friends are online to join their dog pack

SAVE YOUR ADVENTURE ‚Äì CLOUD SAVING
- Your adventure is important! Use the Cloud to back up characters when you register with an account.
- Never lose your progress or miss a save with continuous gameplay across all of your devices.

YOUR FAVORITE DOG BREEDS
- Husky
- Dalmatian
- Daschund
- Doberman
- Boxer
- German Shepherd
- And many more!

Build a family and choose from your favorite dog breeds in this free animal simulator! Download Dog Sim Online and raise your dog family today!

Have fun playing Dog Sim!

If you have any suggestions or ideas for the game - contact us please:
support@turborocketgames.com
We are getting happier with each of your email message.

Please note, that we are in no way affiliated with any other animal simulator games developed by other game companies.

comments: ["One of my all time favourite childhood games. Hasn't had any updated for a while, however I'm not going to complain about that as the company probably isn't working on this game at all anymore anyways, as its quite old. However, it's a pure classic and often gets re-downloaded every couple of months. Servers usually quite inactive, but the most fun people can be met on there. Also, really adorable dogs lol. And - some super fun quests! Definetly worth your time and a fun game to play through.", "I loved this game, in the last few years but after the update no one is on, and there isn't anything else to do after you complete the quests. I love this game and hope that the chat is reworked or something. So it is less lagy, and maybe add new bosses or quest for each area.", "It's a great game. I really love it but nowadays when you try and chat with someone, It will suddenly stop and you are unable to chat with that person. It gets incredibly annoying when you are just trying to talk to someone.", 'I think dog sim is a very nice game and very interesting I have only started leveling in 5 days and I reached 200 (Maximum level) and I have played it for years now and I love it. There are no updates these years so please make updates for it to be more interesting I have played it about 6 years and I still love it the way it is. But TRG ( Turbo rocket games) can you please make an update if you see this? Because these days you only care about your new games such as wildcraft so pls update', 'i really like the details there are free coins now. you can kill bosses to lvl up and get coins and there are no crashes there are many skins. stamina is very useful because you can run attack or jump longer, and who ever created this game is really talented', "It's a great game! In the future, I hope to see more amazing dog breeds, more bosses to kill, and more places to explore! :) And it would also be really cool if you could buy different houses like in cat sim and be able to go upstairs in your house! I would also love to see dog collars you can put on your dogs to customize them more! The only problem I'm having with the game is sometimes enimies spawn inside places you can't get them. Such as the race track. Anyways Amazing game! ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê", "I love this game so muchü§©ü§©ü§©ü§©üòõü§©ü§©ü§©ü§© that I played it for straight one year And it's so fun. I appreciate how you guys made it, but today, when I was playing, my chat box was not opening. I don't know what to do as I forgotüòÖ I am new now, that's why . Please, please fix it , I hope you understand and help me üòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅüòÅ", 'After the update, servers and players have dropped ALOT. there used to be a ton of servers on east (mostly) and now it only dropped to a couple and non of them are english, its like the game got wiped of its playerbase, and sometimes it wont let me play multiplayer cause it keeps saying errorstring. The game just broke for me entirely. Please dont update your other games like this or I wont be able to play any of them', "It's very simple but I enjoy that simple-ness. Just some places could be more enproved.. But for me it's not much of a deal to worry about. Very cute indeed. Would recommend.", "Its the best just like wildcraft it's pretty cool but maybe make the world alot more like wildcraft please like upgrade the game world please other than that it's pretty great and about the ads please not so much ads", 'Just a ü§òüòùü§òExcellentüíØ game. I found a family game of the dods finally I find a family game. But in this game not very realistic version . Hopefully the game is realistic later.', "The game is soo nice but i want to let u add 1 thing, may we have more skin pls? And for rating 5 stars! And 1 problem it's why my friend list dissapears?", "Pls update the game! It's fun but it gets boring after awhile. Here's some ideas I have to make the game a little more interesting, I want to see the upstairs of the house, more breeds, more customization with the breeds, and being able to customize the house. That's all of the ideas i have pls make a few or more possible! The game would be so much better if you did!", 'I love it but it does need a update here are some ideas -more skins -new map -events like in wildcraft -chest to get skins I would love to have some of that in the game', "The game is good it works fine for me on single player but when I switch to multiplayer it kinda lags alot idk if it's just my device", "I love this game but since the updates it's not really fun anymore because there is no free coins anymore and I love getting free coins to see more games", 'This is a very amazing game I like it very much the only problem I have sometimes the mate have got stuck.', "I would give you a 5 star rating it's just the game is a bit sloppy....we need more dog colours and dog breeds And even more places and it needs to be more realistic.And a easier way of getting quest done it takes me forever to get some done and I want to be able to collect things like a collar and I want owners thank for the game hope you can fix this:)!!!!!", "I enjoy it, it's fun. It gets annoying and boring after a while though. Some of the tasks are hard to take care of. It might ask me to attack 3 humans but I'll end up only finding 2 out of the whole map. My dogs constantly get stuck behind something. Oftentimes they phase through whatever is holding them back and they cant go around the obstacle at all bc they're literally inside it. I mostly play the game because one of the dogs looks EXACTLY like my black mouth Cur <3 that's the only reason", "It's not a bad game but it does seem annoying when it comes to the ads in every single gameplay. The varieties of dogs to buy is kinda interesting yet you always have to grind for coins, which takes forever to get more. Even the quest are slow, why do we have to take an hour or so for a quest to pop up? It's agonizing just to wait for a few hours till you get a quest and then after completing it. ANOTHER couple MORE hours for it to load, SERIOUSLY!? It's ridiculously pointless just to wait...-_-", "I love this dog game! The only bad thing is that there is no way to doge a hunters attack and the music is kind of weird and also I don't like where people are shooting dogs it feels wrong and also you can make the houses a little bit more realistic and be able to go in them", "I'm my opinion this is a decent game. There's lots of bugs, glitches, and problems with it though. Poor graphics, theyre decent but can't compare to Wildcraft. Family members always get caught on trees and various parts of the terrain. There's so many glitches and bugs it annoying. This isn't a bad game, it has potential, but it needs a lot of updates. If you update this game as much as Wildcraft it would have even more downloads, and fame!", "I love this game but please add more to the game. Examples-Mix Breeds to play as, different maps, different AI, different places to have as a home, maybe increase the max level, add daily quests, more bosses for each area like wildcraft, maybe add pets. That's all the examples I have for the game as if now, and I know it's very hard to add things to a game, it takes alot of work and time. I'm not forcing you to add these bits just what I would personally want to see in the game. Stay Safe.", 'Amazing. The game is basically "Have fun and farm with friends!", although its rare to see people talk. Back then I was around level 70 with all the skins, but thanks for adding new ones.However, this game can start alot of friendships, but last time I saw the game it was 3+. Now this is going to attract alot of disgusting things to happen! Why though?', "Compared to the cats simulator they made, this one is extremely glitchy, and a bit harder to control. Also there is no Pekingese. :'( overall, the game is like all the other newer simulators they made. Level up, raise a family, fight enemies. The online for this app actually has more people than the cats, which alarms me since it doesnt play as well. But if your a dog lover, its a lot of fun, both online and offline. 3.5 stars", "My experience with this app is great. I've played for only 5 months and I'm level 200! But one suggestion... Could you make it more like cat sim? Like with clothes and hats. There is nothing wrong with this app. Whoever gives it under 4 stars must be insane. All your games are amazing. Thank you for creating these child friendly games. My sister is 6 and is obsessed with it. My parents have to turn the internet off so she can stop playing! Also can you let us go upstairs?? That's all. Merry Xmas", "Actually, not that bad of a game! I've played it a while back and here's a tip: The cow boss is a lot easier especially if you have a family of dogs. It only took my 3 days to get all the skins because of it! I really think it's interesting. I only rated it 4 stars because the game just looks a little bland- Maybe a new map would be great. Other than that, it's worth the download!", "I enjoy the game but when my friend and I try to connect to the same multiplayer group it immediately sends error messages we have tested it out too and since we can't game together we have lost interest in the game. If it was possible I would gladly play it because it is quite a cute game.", "I really love this game but after you get to level 200 it gets a little boring. There need to be updates that add more things. 1) The max level needs to be 300 and I'm on level 200 and I can't upgrade my dog anymore because it says I have to be level 201. 2) More skins. 3) Maybe 1 or 2 new bosses. 4) There needs to be private friend chats like WildCraft. Also my game crashes at least once a day and every time I open the menu in single player there's an ad. Every time I leave a game there's an ad", "It's not a bad game but it does seem annoying when it comes to the ads in every single gameplay. The varieties of dogs to buy is kinda interesting yet you always have to grind for coins, which takes forever to get more. Even the quest are slow, why do we have to take an hour or so for a quest to pop up? It's agonizing just to wait for a few hours till you get a quest and then after completing it, ANOTHER couple MORE hours for it to load, SERIOUSLY!? It's ridiculously pointless just to wait...-_-", 'This game has a lot of potential for expansion, like making the buildings more useful and accessible, adding missions like for example, fight random assigned enemy to get object, then deliver object to get (boss fight/treasure), or like the winter event that was done some years ago, adding a city boss, event bosses related to holidays even but the devs have done little to nothing with this game recently.', "I LOVE THIS GAME! It's so addictive, and a great time killer! The prices for buying coins are PERFECT! Can you guys please add gifting? I would love to gift my friends different dog breeds. I wish I can give this game more than five stars. I REALLY recommend this for dog lovers! Getting coins (for me) is quite easy. I spend them all, and I always get more than 1,000 coins a day. And no, I don't buy them I just play and do my quests. BEST DOG SIMULATER EVER!‚òÜ‚òÜ‚òÜ‚òÜ‚òÜ", 'Even though the game had great graphics it was too hard to control and the game glitched where the animals could hide and run into buildings. It made them impossible to get to. Not to mention they were very hard to find as well.', "Game was alright at first other than ads popping up every time I check my family stats or other family members getting stuck in fences. I liked the different dog breeds on here and the different maps. I decided to register for an permanent so I could log into a different device account. I filled everything out but it kept saying This email is already in use so I tried a different email I have and it said the same thing. Now I can't get an account to come back to if I decide to uninstall. Pls fix", 'This would have five stars but it has problems. 1: Some of the names people have are inappropriate and need to be blocked and they use hashtags and other stuff to say bad words. This needs to stop. 2: When I play in multiplayer with full wifi bars I constantly get disconnected even when I am refreshing lists of who is playing. Frustrating!!!üò° Other than that great game! üòÅ', "Dude what happened to this game. I used to have it on my iPad like 5 or more years ago and I loved it, so I downloaded it on my phone and it sucks butt!! Sure the map is bigger now, but it's way less detailed, and you cant interact with anything, like you used to be able to climb buildings in the junk yard and eat out of trash cans. I'm really sad this game got worse for some reason :(", "This game is my favorite. Now it takes years to change region. Turbo Rocket, WORK ON THIS GAME PLEASE!! I really need it back. I love this app so much, just update it a little more, and work on it. It's like, when I change region it takes 20 hours to change region. It's the best game ver, better than roblox, but just please make the loading only 10 seconds and less ads and actions. Please make it more playeable. Add more skins as well so more people will play it and love it and rate 5 stars.", "This is a really good boredom-killing game that I would recommend to anyone who likes animal simulation games. The reason I only gave it four stars is because you only get thirty quests to complete,and after that you get no more. Also,the dog breeds are kind of expensive. Over all,it's a good time consuming game.", "Everytime I go to the settings menu to add points, the game goes to an ad, and 9.5/10 times, the game freezes, and I have to exit completely, and go back into the game. It's really annoying. And my mate always gets stuck somewhere and can't follow me.", 'This is a great game! There are fun bosses, unique areas, and more custom features. This is not a five-star game, though. I really like the concept of this game. It needs more quests, more action! I know you can do it, make it come to life! Thank you, Turbo Rocket Games!']

title: Pawmates: The Dog Meetup App
description:
Featured on 50+ news and media channels including BlogTO, Narcity, Newsweek, CTV, City News, Global News, Curiocity, and many more

Downloaded more than 50,000 times in 20+ countries

Pawmates is your friendly neighbourhood dog meetup app! Match, chat, and meet with dogs and their owners near you!

Find your pack! Looking to meet with like minded people who love their pets like you do? Look no further! Our matching works just like your favourite meetup apps. Swipe right on pups you like, left on those you don‚Äôt. Once you‚Äôve matched with them, you can chat freely as much as you want, for free. We do NOT believe in pay to message (who wants to do that?)

Our features include:

CREATE YOUR CUSTOM PROFILE
Post photos of your pup, add details about them including their personality, age, breed, and more!

MATCH WITH PUPS
Unlimited free browsing of the cutest dogs in your area! Change your settings to specify the types of dogs and people you want to meet! Find your gang!

CHAT AND MEET
Pawmates matches show up on your custom wheel! Swipe through your match wheel and start chatting with people and their pups!
Connect with pups near you by organizing meet ups!

OUR PET BUSINESS MAP

Looking for the top rated vets, pet food stores, walkers, or anything else related to your pup like the best park in your area? Hop on over to our Pawmates Map and check out every animal business in your area!

Pawmates is here not only to help you meet your new dogpack, but to help with every other need of pet owners and we're growing daily! We want to build the biggest community of dog lovers around the world. So come join our family today!

CONTACT US!
Have questions, problems, or feedback? Feel free to contact us @ Pawmatesapp@gmail.com Or visit us at our Instagram and Facebook pages to win amazing prizes and giveaways!

YOUR PRIVACY IS IMPORTANT TO US
Please read the terms and policies of Pawmates, as well as the privacy policy carefully. All data is handled under the terms and policies of Pawmates privacy policy. More details can be found here: https://pawmatesapp.com/terms-of-service/
summary: Match, chat, and meet dogs and their owners near you

title: Boo - The World's Cutest Dog
description:
You‚Äôve got a new pet ‚Äì Boo, The World‚Äôs Cutest Dog! Play with Boo in the park and cuddle your new fuzzy friend to sleep. Take awesome selfies with Boo and upload them to your BOO-stagram!

Boo, The World‚Äôs Cutest Dog, is here, and he‚Äôs ready to hang out with you, his human! He needs lots of love and attention, and what‚Äôs more fun than loving this cute little fuzzball? Experience a day in the life of Boo ‚Äì Give him a bath before it‚Äôs time to go to the vet. Dress him up in his favorite outfits. Play frisbee with him at the park and cheer him on while he‚Äôs racing against his puppy friends. Make sure he‚Äôs fed well before you tuck him into bed! 

Features:
> Dress Boo up in rockin‚Äô outfits!
> Oh no! Boo‚Äôs not feeling well. Cure him with your special vet tools!
> Have a fun-filled day with Boo at the park!
> Boo‚Äôs hungry! Feed him yummy food to make his tail wag! 
> Ready, set go! Help Boo win the doggy race!
> Let Boo splash around in a bubble bath ‚Äòtil he‚Äôs squeaky clean!
> Play a lullaby for Boo and tuck him into his cozy bed!

To opt out of CrazyLabs sales of personal information as a California resident, please visit our Privacy Policy: https://crazylabs.com/privacy-policy/

title: Duddu - My Virtual Pet Dog
description:
Let us introduce you Duddu, our new dog! He is a super nice dog who lives in a wonderful world full of fun and adventure. Become a part of Duddu‚Äôs everyday life and build a true friendship with your new virtual pet.

‚Ä¢ As a new pet owner, you are responsible for feeding, putting asleep, entertaining and looking after your own dog in his lovely house. In addition, you will have to take care of your scout dog in the wild as well!

‚Ä¢ Oops, Duddu needs doctor's help! Welcome to the animal hospital full of doctor games to give your dog the treatments he needs. Appoint him to the right vet‚Äôs office to solve a problem with fleas, stomach, leg, virus or wound. You can also pick some medicinal herbs and cook potions at the outdoor fireplace.

‚Ä¢ It‚Äôs time for a spa adventure! Have fun in the pool or sauna with Duddu‚Äôs pet friends and enjoy preparing smoothies or coloring mandala in the cutest pet beauty salon. 

‚Ä¢ Visit every corner of Duddu‚Äôs world and all of his friends, too. Take him on vacation to the sunny island with a cosy hammock and coconut palms. Customize your own pirate ship and teach Duddu different tricks at the dog school. Enjoy dancing in the club, exercising in the gym, painting and doodling in the gallery or playing drums and piano in the music centre. Have fun exploring the colorful world where the Sun goes up and down whenever you want.

‚Ä¢ Play over 30 different mini games and earn some coins or other goods. Have fun playing Bubble Shooter, Solitaire, Archer, Pirate Battle, Brick Breaker, Block Puzzle, Treasure Island, Moto Racer, Fruit Connect, Space Explorer, Hen Farm, various cooking games and many others. Go shopping and buy some unique pieces of furniture, food and clothes or customize your pirate ship and your house.

‚Ä¢ Complete daily challenges to learn about the dog‚Äôs habits and become a master of achievements to get some extra rewards. Check your mailbox everyday, you may find a surprise gift from a special friend.

This game is a guaranteed fun for people of all ages. Taking care of a pet gives you a sense of responsibility and loyalty. All you need to begin the fun journey is your own Duddu dog!

This game is free to play but certain in-game items and features, also some of those mentioned in game description, may require payment via in-app purchases which cost real money. Please check your device settings for more detailed options regarding in-app purchases.
The game contains advertising for Bubadu‚Äôs products or some third parties which will redirect users to our or third-party site or app.

This game is certified compliant with the Children‚Äôs Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) by FTC approved COPPA safe harbor PRIVO. If you would like to know more about the measures we have in place for protecting child privacy please see our policies here: https://bubadu.com/privacy-policy.shtml .

Terms of service: https://bubadu.com/tos.shtml

title: Dog Town: Puppy Pet Shop Games
description:
Start your own Dog Town by breeding and collecting dogs. Experience dogs training where your puppies can learn lots of new commands. Train your dog & puppy, send them to quests and funny adventures. Raise your animals and take care of cute puppies in Dog Town simulator games! Pet your puppy, wash, groom, feed like in real life! Enjoy the cute puppy town with unique pet story & training feature. You can get new dog & puppy cards from pet store for your puppy town & collect them. Discover doggy games and customize the rooms where your dogs live! Design your own interiors with hundreds of decorations that you can find in game virtual store. 
 
In Dog Town you can:
 
‚òÖ Train your dogs and teach them lots of tricks with new training feature!
‚òÖ Breed and Collect new dogs! 
‚òÖ Enjoy gorgeous 3D environment! 
‚òÖ Play with realistic Dogs with lifelike behavior!
‚òÖ Take care of your dogs: brush, wash, train, pet & feed!
‚òÖ Level up your dogs and send them to quests!
‚òÖ Decorate your rooms with hundreds of decorations! 
‚òÖ Collect more than 100 dogs and more with each update!
 
If you always wanted to adopt pets or any animal, play with puppies and dogs & were interested in animal shelter, pet & puppy rescue then this is one of the best virtual games for you. Grow your littlest doggo and have fun grooming them . Each animal has a unique character and behavior, so you will always recognize your "Sleepy" from the "Jumpy"! Also you will see their unique behavior while training your puppy. We've put a tremendous amount of effort to ensure that you would feel attached to your animal dogs just like you would to the real ones.
 
In this dog & animal simulation game you can collect dog breeds like: Basset hound, Staffordshire Bull Terrier, Springer Spaniel, Boston Terrier, Labrador Retriever, Australian Shepherd, German Shepherd, Yorkshire Terrier, Bull Terrier, Great Dane, Schnauzer, Cocker Spaniel, French Bulldog, Pomeranian, Doberman, Siberian Husky, Miniature Pinscher, Beagle, Chihuahua, Corgi, Dachshund and other dog breeds. After training your puppies they will become stronger & will participate in more challenging quests. There is a large emphasis on Dog Collection and management for casual and midcore players. 
 
Download now and start having fun with cute pets!
 
 
Enjoyed Dog Town? Join our community:
https://www.facebook.com/groups/382045606113476
 
Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. If you are having any problems in the game or have a great idea about it please contact gamesupport@frismos.com
summary: Cute doggy rescue story, pets & animal care game. Dogs shelter hotel simulator.

title: Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D
description:
Welcome to an amazing life of our furry friend with Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D. Immerse in a dog life simulator, you can see the world through your dog's eyes. You will interact with hundreds of naughty and difficult challenges and have fun with all the perks and pitfalls.

You have to choose the right family. Being a good dog or a naughty dog depends on your decision. Think carefully before making a choice. Make up your mind! Try Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D for FREE now. 

üê∂ How to play Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D:
- Choose and create your favorite dog.
- You are free to make choices that affect the outcome of your dog‚Äôs life.
- Care for your dog and make him happy.

üê∂ Game Features:
- A variety of challenges and opportunities for your dog to explore.
- Smooth and addictive gameplay.
- Awesome 3D graphic.

Don't miss this awesome game for all pet lovers. Download Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D, start your dog life journey now, and see how your dog's stories unfold.
summary: Observe world from dog's eyes in dog life simulator & make the right choices.

title: Dog Simulator
description:
The best MULTIPLAYER Dog Simulator available on Android!

Play as a real puppy - jump, bark, destroy the house and do whatever you want. Now with a multiplayer mode you can play your friends and people all over the world. Cute puppies and fun adventures are waiting for you!

ONLINE MULTIPLAYER
Play online with animal lovers all over the world. Play together with other dogs, meet new friends and compete with them for the best score. See if anyone can match your skills as a naughty dog. You can create your own games which can be joined by your friends.

DOGS AND PUPPIES
If dogs are your favourite pets then this is the game for you. Play as your favourite dog breed: corgi, shiba and husky puppies are waiting for you. If you love bigger dogs select one of the collies, bulldogs or a greyhound to bring even more cuteness to the game. And if that‚Äôs not enough try a wolf, direwolf or a giraffe (well it‚Äôs a sneaky greyhound dressed as a giraffe). 

UPGRADE AND DRESS YOUR DOG
When you press either single player or the multiplayer button in the menu you always go to the scene where you can change your dog and dress it as you like, using blue arrows on the both sides of the dog and buttons on the top of the screen. You can dress your doggy with multiple hats, collars and funny glasses. Then everyone can see your cool outfit in multiplayer games.

LOCATIONS
There are six locations. First, awesome house were you smash some objects and learn the game. Second, nice garden with a dog that will follow you and a grill party to ruin. Third is a shop with lots of objects that can be smashed into pieces. Fourth and fifth are on a huge farm full of animals and people where you can chase sheep to get points. The last one is a crazy town with tons of stuff to destroy and funky missions.

TIME CHALLENGE
In every level in the single player mode there is a rotating clock. When you run into it, you can activate time challenge mode. In this mode you have to destroy as many objects and do as many interactions as fast as possible. For the points you earn the stars and more gold.

NIGHT MODE
Score one star in the last level to unlock a secret night mode. It contains new time challenges for every stage with increased difficulty and even bigger rewards. See if you‚Äôre a true expert.

SIMPLE CONTROLS
You can use the joystick, on the left to move your dog, jump button on the right to make it fly and swipe to look around. You can use the hit button on the right to smash objects with your awesome dog power.

QUALITY SETTINGS
The game will automatically detect which quality settings to apply for your device, but you can change them in the settings menu.

FACEBOOK AND SOCIAL SHARING
At the end of the time challenge, the popup will show up allowing you to post your score on Facebook or Twitter. You can also share the image of your dog on in the scene where you change dogs and dress them.
summary: The most beautiful and realistic Dog Simulator on the Google Play!

title: Tamadog - Puppy Pet Dog Games
description:
Have you ever dreamed about having a dog? About a cute little puppy that you will take care of‚Ä¶ Dreams come true with dog life simulator Tamadog. It is your new virtual pet. Care for it, love and make it happy.

Your new virtual friend üê©

Don‚Äôt hesitate and get a dog right now. Such a lovely, charming and cute puppy, who likes having fun, eating yummies and taking selfies. You‚Äôll never get bored with it. Discover the Tamadog‚Äôs bright world with a variety of exciting adventures in dog town.

Meet your new virtual friend in the Tamagotchi dog game. Just look at these cute eyes that will melt your heart‚Ä¶ Play talking puppy games, give it delicious treats, take it for walks and just have fun all day long. Pet dog games are made for love. Give your doggy all your love and it will definitely love you back.  

Check out the Tamadog pet simulator and enjoy taking care of your little faithful friend. Imagine that you are playing dog sim Tamagotchi - now the gameplay is in the real pet world‚Ä¶ It's a dream come true.

TAMADOG COOL FEATURES:

üê∂ VIRTUAL PET IN YOUR REAL HOME. Don't forget to give your pet care everyday. Feed it, clean and play with it. You can play both 3D and AR games mode. Allow the app to use a phone camera and your puppy will appear right inside your house. 
üêï RAISE A SMART PET. Record voice commands and train your dog. From ‚Äúsit down‚Äù to ‚Äúbreak dance‚Äù ‚Äì you can teach your dog lots of cool tricks. Talk to your friend. You doggy is so sociable and eager to learn. That is my dog - you will say proudly. 
üì∏ CAPTURE AMUSING MOMENTS. Take cute selfies with your puppy and its dog life, make hilarious videos and share them with friends.
üé∞ UNLOCK NEW LEVELS. Keep raising a happy pet, play dog games and enjoy extra activities as a reward.
üëó DRESS UP YOUR PUPPY. Stylish suits for agile male pups and fancy dresses for fluffy girl puppies - dress up your little friend trendy.
ü•∞ ULTIMATE CUTENESS. Your new friend loves you and goes head over heels when you rub its belly. Can you imagine that your doggy will gladly lick your nose anytime you move the screen closer? All possible with animal games. 
üéÆ MINI-GAMES. Your puppy is asleep or you just need to relax from the daily routine? Try yourself in exciting mini-games in a dog simulator and set your records. There are a lot of puppy games for free for any taste: shooting bubbles is just as entertaining as healing and grooming your dog in diverse and enjoyable lovely pets mini-games.

The only virtual dog that looks like and feels like a real dog. Feed it, pet it, play with it. Take it wherever you want, your doggy with its pet‚Äôs world is always at hand. You‚Äôll never get bored with it.

Show everyone how adorable your puppy is. Try to catch all the bright moments spending together with your virtual friend in puppy games. Take amusing and funny selfies with your AR dog and create your own photo album full of happy memories.

Your pet is tired? Take a break - play mini puppy games free to not feel bored. Challenge yourself in exciting Match 3 games, while your pet is resting. Discover more than 300 levels of the game and try to finish all them to earn special gifts for your talking dog. Play dog games for free and make your pet happier.

TRY PREMIUM ACCESS 
Subscribe for Premium and get unlimited access to all the AR dog game features:
üçñ Unlock all premium items
üçñ Unlock AR mode
üçñ Free daily coins and diamonds

Time has come! Get a puppy with the Tamadog pet games. Love it, care for it and make sure it is becoming your best friend. üíó
summary: Have fun with cute puppy games and raise your charming dog!

title: Dog Sled Saga
description:
A game by Dan + Lisa

As a rookie musher, foster a dogsledding team whose skills will grow if they're treated right. Week by week, get to know your dogs' unique traits, and carve your story into the trails of the Mount St. Something region.

Dog Sled Saga has a pick-up-and-play dogsled racing. Each dog's speed is hindered by hunger. Lob a limited supply of food to them to keep at full speed. Hazards on the track await.

By the time you reach the top league, you‚Äôll need to:
- Budget monthly league expenses
- Hire and fire dogs
- Leverage fame to earn sponsorship deals
- Bring on employees for multitasking
- Breed puppies
and more.

Features:
- Pick-up-and-play racing
- Deep team management simulation
- Unique dogs with varying attributes and conditions
- True pixel-grid art style with frame-by-frame animation
- Multi-platform save sync via Drive
summary: Foster a dogsledding team whose skills grow if they're treated right.

comments: ['This game is the best! The graphics are so cute, and gameplay it\'s super fun! However I have two bugs to report. 1. When I go to type (change dog name, etc.) The game freezes. 2. Sometimes, the graphics overlap, so when I\'m in the "Journal" menu, the date and activity icons at the bottom overlap the bottom and make it difficult to read. These are minor problems, so 5 stars :D', "Loved this game when it came out but never got to finish. Came back to it, and sadly the lack of updates have made performance pretty bad. On my Note 10+ in fifteen minutes of gameplay, it froze once and had many, many issues with touch screen responsiveness. :( Hopefully the devs come back to it one day, because the gameplay was always really fun, but it's been three years since the last update, so I guess I shouldn't hold my breath.", "8/10 Really good game, would recommend. Only one problem: When I try to type something in (like a dog's name), the game freezes and has to be restarted. So I can only stick to the randomly generated options. I would hope to see this fixed, but overall it doesn't take much from the experience.", "Great game, I love the dogs, the breeding mechanics, and the story. My singular issue: the game definitely needs some optimization for mobile. Races that require 4+ dogs or have weather events like snow quickly lag, resulting in bad timing and subsequently losing races you shouldn't have a problem in. Even after I ran my phone in developer mode and forced higher processing power, the races still lag. My suggestion: get the game off Steam and play on your laptop. It's well worth it.", "Really fun game! Easy to understand, fun, and nice to look at. You can't pick your own names for the dogs without the game crashing. You can still use the name randomiser and change the harness colour, so it's still pretty good. Also the sound can't be disabled for during races, it's still really loud.", 'I love it but recently ive been getting a bunch of bugs from it, its been lagging alot and just today ive had to restart the app five times because it kept freezing. Its an amazing game and i love playing it nonetheless. The bugs include not registering my touch, clicking multiple times when ive only touched the screen once (a dog got accidentally hired because of this lol), then when i tried to add a sponsor it glitched or something cause it only showed a blue bar where sponsors usually are.', "I've played this game a couple times over the years. The art is super cute and well done. I do feel like the game could use more depth and fun updates. But for what it is it's a cute simple game. I enjoy it, but do get bored with it quickly. The races are very monotonous, I just wish there was more to the game.", "the game gets 5 stars, the port to mobile is what I'm reviewing. playing on a galaxy s9 and its glitchy on the display, the extra length of the s9 screen means there are two bars on the sides that show the background of my phone - very distracting. another glitch is when naming dogs it simply freezes up and you have to restart, so I have a few dogs with some pretty silly random names. a few times in the kennel screen, I have trouble petting or clicking on my dogs. fixes on the way I hope! <3", "This is a very cute game and I absolutely adore the pixel style and that there's a nice selection of dogs to choose for your team. The story is very interesting and I like it. It's a game I always come back to play. The are a few bugs, like the game freezing when I'm selecting dogs or try to change names, on a rare occasion, the game will crash as soon as I launch the app, but that doesn't keep me from trying to play such a nice game. I definitely recommend this game to all my friends.", 'I love this game! Its like it was designed specifically for me lol. Lovely design, fun theme, easy to figure out how to play yet hard enough to keep it interesting. One small glitch is that it crashes when I try to rename the dogs. But overall I just love that this game exists! Long live sled dogs and pixel art :)', "Still has some bugs, Can't type without a freeze and it won't save properly. I tried saving and starting up again and it just brought me back to the very begining. Besides that, I love this game. Hope it gets fixed soon!", 'This game is really fun! I love the dogs and discovering their personalities, but I do have a major problem with the game. It\'s adorable and I love the old school pixel graphics. I've been playing it on my computer for SO long but I really wanted to be able to play it on the go so I finally bought it on my phone. And it's still thrilling to me! And the naming thing doesn't work but that doesn't bother me too much because I can still play the game. :) I hope this gets to the creator of the game because I would really love to see some new updates! The naming bug. Whenever I try to name my dogs, it freezes and I have to shut off my phone just to restart the app.", "I absolutely love the game! The only fault I have with it is that sometimes when I'm racing, once I run out of treats the stations where you refill on treats wont work for me? What I love most about this game is getting new dogs but once I got all the dogs the game just kinda got boring.", 'This is a really good game except the fact that the game freezes when ever I try to type in an ame for a dog,but it will let me use the random option though.', "Dog Sled Saga is the best! The graphics are so cute, and it's so easy to learn. Breeding for certain stats is entertaining. Will definitely recommend.", "I can't write a specific name for a dog or my whole screen freezes I can only choose random names can you maybe fix that if you can? Thank you other then that it's great!", 'I think dog sled saga is a very fun and adorable game it has good graphics and easy to control. Manly there are no adds which makes me really happy. Thanks for making this game.', 'loved the game and it would have been 5 stars but when i breed my dogs and had to name the pup it wont allow me. so now the game is unplayable. pls fix this.', 'Really great game! For the first bit it is really fun game play, and adding to the story is fun, but this game needs an update. After a certain point it is just the same thing over and over again.', 'Do NOT breed two puppies at once I did and now my game is stuck on the "name this puppy" screen and I can\'t do anything about that. My only complaint now is the game won't even load at all its just the blue screen and it won't load", 'I have played this game for about 3 years now and it will not let me rename my dogs or saves. I love the game and would give it 5 star if this gets fixed']

title: Dog Simulator Pet Dog Games 3D
description: Dog Simulator Offline Dog Simulator Pet Dog Games is an open world story based pet simulator game. In the beginning you get the chance to adopt the pet dog of your choice. Later your family will adopt that dog in the family simulator. You will raise the puppy pet by taking care of this dog. Your dog will train to run, jump, play ball and rescue the owners.Offline Dog Game has a complete story mode which shows the progress of your Dog. You can pick any breed of dog, raise your favourite dog. Offline Dog Simulator with amazing controls. Classic dog simulator gameplay. Complete storyline with different modes. Variety of breeds to raise. Plenty of items to give your dog a makeover. Dog Games Pet dog game gives you a chance to train your virtual puppy to be an amazing dog who will complete all the tasks and become the best running dog of the town. Win all the games and make the owners proud. Use your Dog Instincts in this Pet simulator and complete all the tasks one by one. Catch the thief and cats that are stealing food from the house. Complete the tasks and win the heart of neighbours' female dogs to start your own love story. Dog Life Simulator story mode. Virtual Dog Family to raise and take care off. Exciting series of missions and ultimate dog challenge. Dog Run, Dog Jump and Other Exciting Dog Games. Flying Dog Mode We recently have added an open world environment in this offline Dog Game where the dog possesses super powers in which the Dog can fly like a super flying dog, the dog has special attacks which the user can use to eliminate enemies from the city. These enemies will attack you so adopt an aerial route and destroy them. You can also attack the cars in the city. Flying mode is an endless flying mode where you can fly the dog anywhere you want. Take full control of the flight and perform aerial acrobats. Collect special Attacks and attack the enemy from the sky. Open World Environment with Metropolis CIty. Brand New City with Traffic System. Enemy in the open world with enemy AI. Special Attacks and collectables. Roam around the city with no limits Pet Simulator If you like pet games then this dog game is more than perfect for you. Use this animal game to fulfil your needs of having fun. Offline Dog simulator is not an ordinary pet game, animal simulator dog game. You can raise your own pet in these animal games which is a fun task and everyone loves Dogs and this is a golden opportunity for animal games lovers. Pick your favourite dog in a dog game and raise that puppy to a strong dog who wins all the games and performs every task assigned. Become a super dog and fly around the crime city and destroy criminals' cars. As fun family games, enjoy these best in dog simulator games with activities: Play with a pet simulator dog games as family games Training dogs games in the park as virtual games Doggie and master time as fun animal games Enjoy raising pets in this animal simulator. Animal Games Are you in love with the cute dog to make fun of the puppy dog games offline in the world of puppy family simulator games? This puppy world simulator game lets you explore more fun making levels and tasks virtual dog pet cat home adventure. If you find any wandering animal in the dog simulator online. This dog family sim has multi-level tasks to perform against your mother simulator to take revenge in the dog family simulator online 2023. To predict the dogged loyalty in the dog Spiel game, try out the dog adventure game. The animal pet dog world story begins with the adoption of a cute puppy dog in this dog town game offline. Dog game has lots of features to make your time fun when you are alone at home to play in the virtual puppy dog family game.

title: Bumble: Dating App & Friends
description:
Welcome to Bumble üíõ The community with millions of people where you can find dates, make new friends, and meet people.

Bumble is a free dating app and social network for singles; the perfect place to meet new people, in an instant. Whether you want to find friends, make genuine matches, find meaningful connections, chat with strangers, make new friends, or even expand your professional and social network, we‚Äôve got you covered.

Changing the rules of dating

Bumble is a free dating app (to download and use) founded on respect, equality, and inclusion. You can find dates, meet up, and meet new people the way you've always done ‚Äî but on Bumble, women always make the first move. You won‚Äôt find that on any other dating apps. üïí With heterosexual matches, women have 24h to start a chat, and men have 24h to respond üí¨ Other matches (LGBTQIA+) have 24h to start a chat or reply before the match expires üë• Bumble comes in 3 modes to suit what you're looking for: Date, BFF, and Bizz

Discover our amazing features

Meet new people, make new friends, or find a great date using our free dating app. We‚Äôve levelled up from the days of dating sites, and now you have all these features at your fingertips: üëâ Unlimited Swipe: Meet new people by swiping left and right as much as you like üí¨ Unlimited chat so you can find the right matches üéµ Link your Spotify and Instagram account to share your interests with potential dates and friends üìπ Use Video Chat to get to know your matches better

Match with the right people

We're the first app to combine dating for singles, meeting new people, and making professional connections all in one app. We‚Äôre different from other dating apps, because we make it easy for you to connect. üìπUse Video Chat to get to know your matches better üì∑ Send your videos and favorite pictures while you are chatting with new friends üí§ With Snooze Mode, hide your profile whenever you want (you'll still keep all your matches!) üéµ Link your Spotify and Instagram account to share your interests with potential dates and friends

Boost your dating life with Bumble Premium

Bumble is a free dating app to download and use, and always will be! Our Premium features help you enhance your Bumble experience. üíõ See everyone who swiped right on you (your Beeline) üîÅ Rematch with expired connections for a second chance at a date üîÑ Extend your matches by 24 hours The buzz is real Bumble is much more than just a dating app for singles, or your average speed dating night. Join our like-minded dating community, meet new people, find your ideal partner or date. Here are our core values: üíõ We believe healthy relationships are fundamental to living a productive and positive life üíõ In the fight against old-fashioned hetero-norms, women always take the first step. üíõWe've changed the rules of the game to switch up the dynamics of dating üíõUnlike other dating apps, kindness is at the core of everything we do Inclusivity is key We‚Äôre committed to being totally inclusive, and supportive of our community whatever their gender, sexual orientation, or religion. Whether you‚Äôre looking for a place to find friends, a gay dating app, a bisexual dating app, a lesbian dating app, an LGBTQ dating app, a Christian dating app or a Jewish dating app; We‚Äôve got everything you‚Äôre looking for in our lovely community. --- Bumble is a dating app that is free to download and use. We also offer optional subscription packages (Bumble Boost and Bumble Premium) and non-subscription, single, and multi-use paid features (Bumble Spotlight and Bumble SuperSwipe). Your personal data is securely stored on Bumble - be sure to read our privacy policy and terms and conditions https://bumble.com/en/privacy https://bumble.com/en/terms Bumble Inc. is the parent company of Bumble, along with the dating apps Badoo and Fruitz. Enjoy all our dating apps!
summary: The dating app to meet new people, chat and date with singles or make friends!

comments: ["It is a total waste of time and money. It does not matter if you have premium, you won't be receiving any matches at all (I had subscribed to the premium, still the same). It's like a window shopping app where you just keep scrolling and scrolling until you're satisfied without hoping to get anything. For once I thought this app could be genuine and I purchased the premium, but no, if all I had to do was left and right swipe people, I might have as well stayed on Tinder for free.", 'The UI is quite user friendly. But few things which can be improved on. 1. Message notification doesn\'t pop up a lot of times 2. Call notification doesn\'t pop up ever, plus call drops multiple times 3. Filter option doesn\'t work properly, for example if I choose age range 33-36, I still see people of age 23 4. Algo for common interest can be improved specially for best bees feed, I get best bees who want "Something Casual" while my preference is "Relationship"', 'Totally wast of time & Money, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', "1. Poor algorithm. When you don't have premium, it shows you all persons within small distance. Once you subscribe to premium, the people shown would be around 100 km. Very few local profiles are shown. So the developer's motive seems to attract people to Premium subscription by showing good profiles, then serve trash. 2. Even though I cancelled the subscription in advance, it charged me for another month and didn't give premium features. 3. Useless app. Never coming back.", 'As a long-time user of Bumble, my recent experience has been disappointing. Despite being active, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', "Its definitely a good app, but could use a few improvements. I don't use premium, but I don't mind it much so far. Anyhow, I do find it irritating that women always have to make the first move. I get why Bumble chose to do so, but it's irritating I always have to text first, especially since matches expire. Sometimes I get busy or forget to check the app, and I lose a lot of matches. I think it'd be nice sometimes if the other person could also text first.", 'Waste of time and money, the location of people is totally hit and miss, when you do "match" with someone it is debatable if they are actually real or generated by the app to keep you interested. For an app that is meant to compliment your social circle/find people with similar interests and so on, no one actually talks. Might just stick with the old-fashioned way!', 'I can not escape the feeling of a jacked up algorithm. One that puts people on the bottom despite their subscription in some sort of "lead with a carrot" business model. That or no one\'s on this app, and the app does not seem to want to take people who have not been on the app in months in the algorithm. Furthermore, there seems to be no quick, obvious, and easy way to end your subscription.', "I used the app for about one year and had a few decent dates out of it. However, as soon as my paid membership expired, literally overnight, I went from having zero people interested in me to 47, of course being prompted to go back to the paid version. Didn't change location or filters during that time, so obviously, they are manipulating the truth and the end user.", 'For an app that requires access to your location, you\'d think they\'d give you an accurate mileage estimate for people near you, but nope they can\'t be bothered to do that. Just saw someone who lives in the next state over from me and, according to Bumble, they\'re 85 miles away from me. However, when I enter the city on Google maps, it gives me a much more accurate mileage: 156 miles. That\'s a 71 mile difference, nearly double Bumble\'s "estimate."', 'The worst of all dating apps. Like Tinder, gives you options from ridiculous distances, especially if youre in rural areas. Most people are visitors from very far. The worst part is once youve swiped left on a potential match they are removed from your likes and you probably will never see them again."you\'ve missed a potential match" forever. Also they put the location at the bottom so you have to scroll the whole profile just to see the distance factor. Overall a very bad experience', "This app is ok but needs work. I canceled my premium. One of the big thing that must be added is letting me know when the last time a person logged on. That way I'm not wasting time on someone who hasn't logged on in a month. That's a waste of a swipe especially a super swipe. Also need to separate straight people from gay. As I have swiped on the wrong person and they get all offended. If these things were fixed I would keep logging in.", "Terrible app! you have to pay for basic Things like just to see who liked you you can only see the people that complimented your profile and that's limited, You have to pay for everything like super swipes & to go back if you made a mistake. They took down one of my photos for going against community guide lines but it's a picture of me in a long dress no nudity nothing inappropriate. & whatever preferences youre allowed to choose (age and distance) doesn't narrow down the field", "Still an awful app, I've tried it multiple times and men never see their related matches. We get search results from 97 miles away from people who don't match our criteria. And you can tell even from the blurry images that you never see the people who actually do swipe on you. It's entirely designed to keep you swiping without any actual results. Don't waste your time", 'It\'s just as bad if not worse than Tinder surprisingly. Customer service is 0/10. I can\'t get a hold of any humans to discuss my problems, I\'ve sent at least 10 emails. I get photos randomly taken down because they "violate" community standards according to the algorithm. I\'ve purchased the lifetime membership twice and, like anyone, deleted and reinstalled the app many times, but now I dont have the lifetime membership, and they won\'t fix it. Summary: All dating apps suck.', "I think it's more likely to get struck by lightning and win the lottery at the same time than get a match. It's way too easy to accidentally swipe left, and those swiped on can't come back, and the highlights cost 8 bucks each. Like, who even? Fix your app.", "What's the use of having the dating interface if you can't even contact/connect to a prospect without having to pay a bloody fee? And even then, even if you do want to spend on it, the chances of getting catfished is unbelievably high. The aspect of this side of the app is completely useless. I will give it props if you're using it for business networking purposes and works well if that is your ONLY objective. The dating interface is bonkers.", "it's very picky and decisive wanting you to spend money just like any other app. they shouldn't just give the option free to connect with anyone but they should make a lot easier if you want to say hello or block or do what you would like explicit or not. there's filters for everything. just make it all around app that everybody can use. it's 2023 and this is the longest run on sentence I've ever done. but we all know what we're looking for in the beginning and in the end and who may b in middle", "All the other dating apps I get plenty of matches, but bumble is awful at what it's supposed to do. No matches, and because of the time limit to message you often miss the matches you do get. Pointless app and a waste of time. Edited, after the reply I received more likes than before after I left a review, strange, then they started to get less and Ive just realised the compliment feature has been removed. I think the free compliments were the only thing that made bumble worth using.", "Because you can't filter results by important categories like religion without paying, the app is essentially useless. You are forced to weed through thousands of profiles that aren't close to your value specifications. The profiles layout is also a mess, listing interests in a buckshot-style jumble where things like children, religion, age, location, etc are thrown into the mix randomly and you have to look around more to find it (those should be at the top of the list).", "It's...ehhh. My issues are the inability to filter out poly/ENM profiles looking for unicorns, continuing to get likes from men when I am a lesbian, the constant message ads and empty notifications, and the high cost of premium. Been using it for a few months now, met one potential person but I'm demoralized. I won't renew my subscription.", "Bumble is useless without a premium subscription. All filters except age & distance are now locked behind a paywall, so rooting through all the bad matches to find someone is a chore. You only get 24 hours to respond to a match, otherwise you have to pay to rematch. And if you accidentally swipe left on someone you do want to match with, you have to pay to undo it. If the woman matches but doesn't start chatting within 24 hours, (Something that happens A LOT) the match disappears completely.", "The customer service for Bumble is absolutely terrible!! I have contacted them over 10 times in a two week span and Bumble has not replied to ANY of my inquiries. My account is stuck on photo verification and I cannot access any othet part of my account. I am currently paying for the Premium option as well. Don't use this app - they dont care about you at all.", "Not sure how I feel about it. So far I like how the verification process goes and the app runs smooth but been on it for 2 weeks with premium and not worth it. You don't really get as much people due to the fact that the premium is expensive and also the notification when you do get someone doesn't really appear on either the app notification or email. Also anyone you've liked you can't tell if they even seen the like. Definitely needs more work for the cost.", "I like this app, in my opinion it' s very nice but it's just ridiculously expensive. probably the most expensive app I've tried. so I subscribed in different app although I still use the free features on Bumble. Some things could be better. don't like the fact that only match girls can do first move, think that's silly. I've been on a date with a girl and she complained that men never say anything, then I said we can't, first move has to be from girl.", "When you pay to upgrade and it run out. I have found that when you get likes the system doesn't match you with them. I wants you to upgrade. They then timed out and their gone. Don't pay for the upgrade or you'll just have to delete your account like I did. It should be above all, about finding a connection.", 'Having a limit on likes per day isn\'t a bad idea, but this app\'s limit is almost cartoonish. I can\'t spend more than a few minutes per 24 hours swiping without being told I need to pay 3 WHOLE DOLLARS to keep going. It\'s asinine. On top of that, almost everything else is locked behind paywalls. Though I do like that you can list your pronouns without having to first pick "man or woman." But that\'s just basic decency, not a feature', "I've been on Bumble for a few weeks now. Ended up paying for the boost, matched with someone who, for their prompt, asked me to verify my photo. Prior to this I had tried probably 20 times to verify, and was never able to. Yes I tried photos with just myself. Mimicking the pose, hand gestures, and even location exactly, but couldn't verify. Now I'm stuck on the verification screen, I'm being ignored by the support team. 0/5", "To the pros: fairly clean & simple UI, tho a bit outdated. Cons: gps based search, meaning swiping endlessly tons of people in proximity, including tourists & people in the airport and there's no way to filter out. And you have to scroll all way down to find out person is living somewhere else or doesn't disclose. So looks like tinder at this point and more oriented towards finding one night stand nearby. Exhausting & very disappointing experience for me and after a long time trying it, I'm out", "Even after having premium it doesn't let's text to someone who liked my profile. It clearly showed in best bees match. But it didn't let me text. What a pathetic app. They just want you to keep browsing and keep paying for super swipes or compliments even after buying premium. You will get nothing here. I think they just got some profiles when they launched the app. Might be no longer active because this app doesn't let people text even after liking from both sides.", "Bamble has completely changed my dating game! The interface is so user-friendly and the profiles are detailed. I've had some great conversations and even met up with a few matches. The safety features make me feel comfortable putting myself out there ..", 'Sent a support message because the app was malfunctioning and did not hear back. Super frustrating as it\'s deleted messages, not notified me about matches, and given me at least 20 "ghost matches." Meaning that it tells me that I have \'seconds left to reapond\' and never see a match or any reference to one when I log in. 8/18 Update: Messaged the support team on FB yesterday like the moderator suggested and haven\'t heard back.....', "The app generally is easy to navigate. But it works on Likes. If a person likes another person, that other person will not see the profile of whom has 'Liked them, unless they subscribe. I tried with and without subscription, if you don't pay you don't see the 'Liker'. I think there is misunderstanding of this being like Facebook and folk randomly 'like' . Bumble needs the 'how long since been active' or filter out the 'non-users' somehow. The speed dating is awful üòñ Get rid or show a pic.", "The facial recognition and it's term in this app is sucks!! My profile pics is exactly as my now i take, but still wrong! Why not verify person in manually like the other app dating? AI mostly can be wrong! And the face fiture of people can change as the time always change. Hope this app can use other method to verified person!!", "So I decided to buy a week of premium. It's not worth the $20. Once it's gone you just get people that don't match your filters. Having to pay to filter people based on important things like having or wanting kids in the first place is pretty sleezy. They also take away any spotlights you have left over when premium expires. The distance filter doesn't look at where people live, and is terrible for people looking for long-term. Prepare to either pay too much for Bumble or be disappointed.", "My biggest complaint is there's no swipe priority to people who superswiped. It'll give me a notification that I got superswiped but it'll take me days to find out who actually did it. I would greatly appreciate if you could fix that as pretty much every other app places priority on that stuff and not having it makes superswipes seem kinda useless.", 'Would never recommend, because of 0 support. Wrote 5 times - no response. Bought a lifetime Premium. Had to simply reinstall the app, and now the premium purchase is gone, verifying is not possible (just shows "Oops" on their website). Have sent various requests, almost a week past - no answer. Waste of money.', "Terrible. I tried the BFF part and every woman I matched with is terrible at communicating. It doesn't seem like anyone is serious about making friends even though their profile says it. They all take over 1-2 days to reply or not at all and they even messaged me first. I ask open ended questions too. It seems people are just looking for validation by matching. If you're looking for genuine friendships, this ain't it. These people are fake and some are just looking for IG followers.", "Don't buy the spot lights!!!! The app will self activate them and email support stopped trying to help! I tried just not being on for a couple days till subscription weekly one was added when I did log on it has already used it and times out! Yes I emailed them and they tried a couple time but stopped helping. Lost 5 so far. And they are not doing anything to help. Very disappointed in you guys. I'm done I've cancelled the subscription and not trying to get your help when you just blow it off.", "I would like to love this app, but it is actively keeping matches apart. I purchased the unlimited likes package and swiped through everyone in my area, yet it still says there are people that like me nearby even though I can not swipe on anyone else. It's just trying to make me but the ability to see my likes. They don't care about people getting into relationships they just care about money. If you do get this app, don't spend any money on it because it's only worth the free content"]

title: My Puppy Friend - Cute Pet Dog
description:
If you are a pet lover, these cute puppies would definitely melt your heart!

Your love and care could make the little ones' life different! Take them home and feed them with delicious food. Or give them a shower to wash off the dirt. A stylish makeup pairing with a chic outfit will help the pets stand out in the show, which would award you with a lot of decorations and take the puppies' home up a notch! Parkour, seek out the bones‚Ä¶many fun activities are ready to blow your mind!

Features:
- 6 cute puppies that melt your heart
Life gets a whole lot more interesting if you take these little cuties home. 
- Collet loving hearts to open the Show where you may get decorations
Each time you complete a mini game, one heart would be awarded to you. With 3 hearts, you can join the Show and win the decorations.
- Earn coins and exchange them for nice items
Take the challenges with your pets to earn as many coins as you can and exchange them for food, outfits and other nice things.
- Fun-filled mini games work well with the amazing scenes
Have fun with your doggies in such gorgeous scenes and wonderful activities.

About Libii Game:
With over 600 million downloads and growing, Libii is committed to creating innovative games for kids. We'll keep working on establishing a good relationship with both parents and their children and bringing a healthy, happy atmosphere for them.
Visit us: http://www.libii.com/
Like us: http://www.facebook.com/LibiiGame
Contact us: Got any ideas? Suggestions? Need technical support? Please feel free to contact us 24/7 at WeCare@libii.com

Need You Know:
This app is totally free to download and play, some basic items are also free to use, but some additional items need you to purchase and pay to unlock. Therefore, if you do not want to use these items, please turn off the in-app purchase in your settings. Thanks.

title: Dog Training App ‚Äî GoDog
description:
POSITIVE-BASED DOG TRAINING. BUILT-IN DOG CLICKER. TRAIN YOUR DOG ANYTIME, ANYWHERE!

Are you a happy dog owner? Do you want to know how to train your dog in easy-to-follow steps? Download GoDog ‚Äî smart guide for dog training and taking good care of your pet.

Here you will find a full lesson‚Äôs pack with step-by-step video instructions verified by professional dog trainers, built-in dog whistle and clicker, health and care diary, time walking schedule, useful articles, and other features that help your dog stay healthy and happy!

DOG TRAINER APP
These are easy-to-grasp and reproduce lessons for your dog that assist you with essential behavioral training. Teach your puppy to be socialized and well-adjusted without overpaying for dog trainer‚Äôs services. All lessons are made together with highly qualified dog trainers. 

You will find different lesson packages, such as Basic (sit, down, stay, no, paw), Good Pup Behavior (come, stop barking, chewing, don‚Äôt jump), Puppy Training Course (potty, collar, come on leash), Dog Tricks and Games, etc. We offer basic lessons for free.

HEALTH DIARY FOR KEEPING YOUR FURRY FRIEND FIT
With the GoDog Health & Care Diary, you'll never forget to take care of your pet. Create reminders for vaccinations, medications, visits to the vet, and other important events in your dog's life and save a history of these events. Track the hygiene care of your doggy including bathing, teeth brushing, nail clipping, ear cleaning, etc. Define dog schedule and let the GoDog app remind you when the next action is due.

WHISTLE AND CLICKER FOR TRAINING DOGS
Use these features to improve and strengthen the results of your dog training exercises. Dog clicker training is gaining popularity for its ease of use and positive effect. Download GoDog and use our built-in dog clicker with 3 different sounds!

WALKING TRACKER
Keep an eye on how much exercise your dog gets on a daily basis. It will help you adjust your walking routine to your dog‚Äôs specific needs.

DOG HEALTH ARTICLES
It‚Äôs extremely important to read up-to-date and verified information so as not to harm the dog. All information and articles in GoDog are checked by professional canine experts and vets, so you can have a rest, while learning something new about your fluffy friend.

Download the GoDog app now and start dog training and spending quality time with your four-legged friend!

Please feel free to contact us: info@godog.me
Privacy Policy: https://www.godog.me/privacy-policy

title: Dog Whisperer: Fun Walker Game
description:
Dogs are man‚Äôs best friend. It‚Äôs true, we love them a lot. And dogs need to be walked. But the neighborhood is full of dangers and obstacles. Dog owners are waiting for their dogs, can you help them reunite?

- Just swipe up and run.
- Collect dogs and give them to their owners.
- Different player types.
- Run with rollerblades!
- Casual, rare, and unique dog breeds.
- Casual, classy, and epic player types.
- Unlock new things in store.
- Rescue dogs!

Man‚Äôs best friend!
Retriever, Akita, Bull Terrier, Pug, Dalmatian and so much more. All of them are lovely. Help them to find their owners and enjoy running with dogs with rollerblades on your feet. There are lots of dog breeds in Dog Whisperer. Let‚Äôs run to meet them!

Who are you?
Walking a dog is fun, especially if you can choose your character! Unlock new players from among different characters, put on your rollerblades, and start running. Dogs want to run and owners want to meet their dogs.
summary: Rollerblade around town to catch dogs and reunite them with their owners

title: Merge Dogs
description:
Merge your dogs, build the ultimate dog racing team and win the race!

Do you have what it takes to be the best dog racer out there? Start by getting small puppies, then upgrade them into bigger faster dogs and earn lots of money!

Features:
- Over 20 different dog breeds to discover including shiba inu, corgi, golden retriever, pug, french bulldog, chihuahua, poodle, beagle, dachshund, dalmatian, dobermann, rottweiler and lots more!
- Idle earnings. Gain coins even while you are away or offline.

Manage your team of super fast dogs. Start your dog racing team now and become a champion!
summary: Build your doggy team and win the race!
